result.name: Sushi Express

reviews.text:
Great place, with tasty food. The staff were kind to accommodate us and the language barrier wasn't too obvious (they're quick to find somebody who speaks English in the times of need).

The sushi was great and very affordable. 10/10 would recommend.
Not many choices but it's cheap and tastes good. Conveyor belt fills up very quickly, count your plates carefully cos staff counting plates is not that good, count more than you actually had.
Travelled to Hong Kong to do a exhibition, tried out this sushi bar, excellent value for money would be 5* if the sushi variety was better.
